    76‚Üí
    77‚Üí         Specifies what to do when a forward reference fails to resolve.
    78‚Üí
    79‚Üí         Default: ``WARN``
    80‚Üí
    81‚Üí    .. attribute:: collection_check_strategy
    82‚Üí       :type: CollectionCheckStrategy
    83‚Üí
    84‚Üí         Specifies how thoroughly the contents of collections (list, dict, etc.) are
    85‚Üí         type checked.
    86‚Üí
